00:00:21.380 --> 00:00:22.400
PARUL SOI: Privacy.

00:00:22.400 --> 00:00:26.060
Specifically, we want to talk
to you about certain practices

00:00:26.060 --> 00:00:28.100
that you as app
developers can adopt

00:00:28.100 --> 00:00:30.200
to build products
that continue to wow

00:00:30.200 --> 00:00:34.380
your users, at the same time,
protect their right to privacy.

00:00:34.380 --> 00:00:36.320
We want Android to
be a platform where

00:00:36.320 --> 00:00:39.110
you can offer
personalized experiences

00:00:39.110 --> 00:00:41.590
